data.name: cmdEDCDDownloadID.ToolTip
data.value: Downloads the latest information of the used IDs by the companion interface from https://github.com/EDCD/FDevIDs (commodities.csv, outfitting_csv, shipyard.csv) They are saved in the data folder with a "EDCD" prefix.

data.name: cmdImportSystemsAndStations.ToolTip
data.value:
Imports the data of systems, stations and commodities from EDDB files ("system.json", "stations.json", "commodities.json", optional "listings.csv"). Suggestion is to import all three files to avoid missing dependences.
Download from "https://eddb.io/api"
